headline: How Recent Developments Are Reshaping The AutoZone Investment Story
summary: AutoZone stock has seen its fair value estimate nudged down to about $4,369 from roughly $4,579 as analysts factor in a slightly higher discount rate of around 8.97% versus 8.75% previously, reflecting a more demanding rate backdrop. While revenue growth expectations have inched higher to approximately 7.85% from 7.82%, recent street commentary balances near term margin and cost headwinds against resilient demand and confidence in the company’s long term earnings power. Stay tuned to see how...
